    "description": "Join the Kale Consultants family as a Frontend Developer in Nagpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Kale Consultants:\nKale Consultants is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kale Consultants!",
